cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is primarily focused on deep neural networks and their capacity, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses advanced training skills such as dropout and batch normalization, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel measurement for evaluating neural network capacity, which involves techniques related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
